{"tid":2075882,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲青年長期通宵打機　突感頭痛入院確診腦中風","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T07:02:30.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"046a0bc1848182f54cd303349c66c8df2fc58a91","tid":2075882,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"廣東深圳市一名18歲陳姓少年近日突然感覺頭痛、頭暈及嘔吐，送院後確診為腦中風。原來，他平日經常通宵打機，導致靜脈堵塞引致腦中風。隨後，醫院為他進行手術。目前，陳男情況已有好轉。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，院方對陳男檢查時，發現其顱內有血栓堵塞血管，而陳男有腎臟病史，而且在發病前一日曾喝酒，加上他經常熬夜玩遊戲，因而發病。陳在剛入院時，精神恍惚、頭痛欲裂，若不及時進行手術，會有性命危險。<br />\n<br />\n該院神經內科副主任醫生賀雄軍表示，中風患者近年有年輕化趨勢，並指自己亦曾接收一名年約10歲的病人。他續指，部分年輕人工作壓力大、沒有控制對自身的危險因素、自以為身體年輕等，導致出現高血壓或其他系統的問題。他提醒市民，要應定期接受健康檢查，並且保持適量運動，減少熬夜及喝酒。"},{"pid":"99c8265e33fc72eeb8eb6e88a0455f2956566e66","tid":2075882,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f1/When_he_flu_he_still_jj.jpg/revision/latest/top-crop/width/360/height/450?cb=20090709021302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff1%2FWhen_he_flu_he_still_jj.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Ftop-crop%2Fwidth%2F360%2Fheight%2F450%3Fcb%3D20090709021302&h=3d755f54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0778810482c227b2454c3912bda78a5b62c6e0d","tid":2075882,"uid":195827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"佢一定通宵打the last of us 2<br />\n好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118ad75947817dcf5b28a745ac07e09024675637","tid":2075882,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"99c8265e33fc72eeb8eb6e88a0455f2956566e66","tid":2075882,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f1/When_he_flu_he_stil